    <description>
      AspNetCoreErrorKit is a flexible, modern exception handling toolkit for ASP.NET Core (.NET 8). 
      It provides global middleware and filter-based exception handling, custom error responses, async logging, and telemetry integration.
      Easily plug into your pipeline for robust error management in your web APIs and MVC applications.
    </description>
    <tags>aspnetcore exception-handling middleware filter error-handling logging telemetry .net8</tags>
    <releaseNotes>
      Initial release: 
      - Exception handling middleware and filter
      - Custom error handlers
      - Async logging and telemetry support
      - Easy DI and extension methods
    </releaseNotes>
    <repository type="git" url="https://github.com/bugzyGeek/AspNetCoreErrorKit"/>
